T02TD3624E:244b-1: tree lo kya bi dza ya s'a dha nam /
T02TD3624E:244b-3: 'jig rten gsum las rnams par rgyal ba'i sgrub thabs //
T02TD3624E:244b-4: dpal ldan rje btsun 'jig rten gsum las rnam par rgyal ba la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3624E:244b-5: 'dir dang po ma skyes pe rnams la sngon du gsungs pa'i chogs nyid ma la h'um yig nag po las skyes pa'i rjes btsun 'jig rten gsum las rnam par rgyal ba sku mdog mthing nag zhal bzhi ba /
T02TD3624E:244b-7: zhal dang po khro zhing sgeg pa //
T02TD3624E:244b-10: rgyab zhal dpa' bo'i nyams can //
T02TD3624E:244b-11: phyag gnyis kyis rdo rje dril bu dang bcas shing /
T02TD3624E:244b-12: thugs kar h'um mdzad kyi phyag rgya bsnams pa /
T02TD3624E:244b-13: g-yas kyi phyag rnams kyis ral gri dang /
T02TD3624E:244b-16: g-yon gyi phyag gsum gyis gzhu dang /
T02TD3624E:244b-19: zhabs g-yon brkyang bas dbang phyug chen po'i mgo mnan pa /
T02TD3624E:244b-20: zhabs g-yas kyis goo r'i'i nu ma zung mnan pa /
T02TD3624E:244b-21: sangs rgyas me tog phreng ba la sogs pa sna tshogs pa'i rgyan dang /
T02TD3624E:244b-22: na bza' bsnams par bdag nyid bsgoms nas /
T02TD3624E:244b-23: phyag rgya bcing bar bya ste /
T02TD3624E:245a-0: de la khu tshur gnyis rgyab sbyar nas mthe'u chung @245a * //
T02TD3624E:245a-1: lcags sgrog gi rnam par sbyar bar bya'o //
T02TD3624E:245a-5: grihn'a pa ya grihn'a pa ya h'um /
T02TD3624E:245a-7: bha ga b'an bidy'a r'a dza h'um phat /
T02TD3624E:245a-8: 'jig rten gsum las rnam par rgyal ba'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so //
